          <p>
            The DJI Osmo Pocket 3 is a masterpiece of engineering. It puts a
            massive <strong>1-inch sensor</strong>
            into a tiny gimbal handle.
          </p>
          <p>
            The low-light performance blows action cameras out of the water, and
            the mechanical gimbal is far smoother than electronic stabilization.
            The snappy <strong>rotatable screen</strong> makes vertical social content
            effortless.
